title: Vampire - Darkstalkers Collection (Japan).7z
description: Vampire: Darkstalkers Collection is an accumulation of 5 different arcade titles from Capcom's Darkstalkers series. Released in Japan in 2005 for the Playstation 2, the game has been released two additional times with one release being a bundle with Street Fighter II: Anniversary Edition. The game also includes several "Arranged" versions of its original games that include the new character, Dee
